<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Black&family=Lato:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
    * {
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: "Lato", sans-serif;
}
.containier {
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 70px;
}
body {
    background-color: #181832;
    width: 100%;
}
.nav-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
}
.nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
}
.nav-logo {
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-size: 24px;
}
.nav-logo span { 
    color: #7777FB;
}
.nav-link {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    list-style: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #181832;
    padding: 8px;
    transition: .3s linear;
}
.nav-link:hover {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #7777FB;
}
.nav-btn{
    background-color: #7777FB;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 12px 32px;
    font-size: 16px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: .2s linear;
}
.nav-btn:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px #7777FB;
    transform: scale(1.2);
}

.header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 80px 0 120px;
}
.header-title{
    font-size: 72px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-weight: 900;
}
.header-title span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b804b8 0%, #3b82f6 50%, #06b6d4 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-size: 90px
}
.header-subtitle{
    color: #0437B8;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin: 24px 0 12px;
}
.header-text {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 24px;
}
.header-btns{
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
}
.header-first--btn{
    background: #5D5DFA;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 12px 32px;
    border: 1px solid #2A2AFB;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: .3s linear;
}
.header-second--btn{
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 12px 32px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: .3s linear;
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    background: none;
}
.header-img img{
    border-radius: 100%;
    width: 700px;
    border: 5px solid #3b82f6;
    border-radius: 20px;
}
.header-subtitle {
    color: #7777FB;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin: 24px 0 12px;

    display: inline-block;
    overflow: hidden;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-right: 3px solid orange;
    letter-spacing: 2px;

    width: 0;

    animation:
        typing 4s steps(22) infinite alternate,
        blink-caret .75s step-end infinite;
}

@keyframes typing {
    from {
        width: 0;
    }
    to {
        width: 19ch;
    }
}
.about{
    margin: 0 0 120px;
}
.about-top{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
}
.about-btn{
    color: #b804b8;
    font-weight: bold;
    border: 2px solid #b804b8;
    background: #181832;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 20px;
}
.about-title{
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 900;
}
.about-top--text {
    color: #ffffff;
}
</style>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="nav">
        <div class="containier">
            <div class="nav-wrapper">
                <h2 class="nav-logo"><span>A.</span>Karimov</h2>
                <ul class="nav-links">
                    <li class="nav-link">Bosh sahifa</li>
                    <li class="nav-link">Men haqimda</li>
                    <li class="nav-link">Ko'nikmalar</li>
                    <li class="nav-link">Loyihalar</li>
                    <li class="nav-link">Xizmatlar</li>
                    <li class="nav-link">Bog'lanish</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="nav-btn">Aloqa</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <div class="header-info">
                <h1 class="header-title">
                    Azizbek__<br><span>__Karimov</span>
                </h1>
                <h3 class="header-subtitle">Frontend dasturchi</h3>
                <p class="header-text">React, TypeScript va zamonaviy dizayn yordamida tez, chiroyli va foydalanuvchiga qulay veb ilovalar yarataman. Keling, loyihangizni birgalikda hayotga olib chiqamiz.</p>
                <div class="header-btns">
                    <button class="header-first--btn">Loyihalarini ko'rish</button>
                    <button class="header-second--btn">CV yuklab olish</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="header-img">
                <img src="mening-rasmim.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="about">
                <div class="about-top">
                    <button class="about-btn">Men haqimda</button>
                    <h2 class="about-title">Salom, men Azizbek</h2>
                    <p class="about-top--text">Zamonaviy veb ilovalar yaratishga ishtiyoqmand frontend dasturchiman.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
